{"tid":1656572,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制風波未息，暴雪取消《Overwatch》Switch版發售活動","createTime":"2019-10-15T15:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T10:54:16.000Z","uid":41818,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ccd32e4a21520f4d85fb8d731d62b429191f6be","tid":1656572,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Katy/2019-others/1571138485801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FKaty%2F2019-others%2F1571138485801.jpg&h=3daffb47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘管暴雪總裁已減輕《爐石戰記》大師職業賽禁賽事件懲處，海內外網路與論壇抵制暴雪（Blizzard）聲浪仍未平息。紐約任天堂旗艦店於今（15）日於官方 Twitter 宣布，《鬥陣特攻》（Overwatch）Nintendo Switch 版發售紀念活動被暴雪下令取消。<br />\n<br />\n《鬥陣特攻》在 9 月宣布將在本月 16 日登上 Nintendo Switch 平台，此版本將囊括 31 位英雄、28 張地圖、15 個造型、外加 3 個月的 Nintendo Switch Online 會員資格（連線遊玩使用）。遊戲還沒發售就碰上「聰哥禁賽」事件，暴雪也受到巨大的輿論壓力。<br />\n<br />\n紐約任天堂旗艦店宣布取消《鬥陣特攻》Nintendo Switch 版發售紀念活動後，不少網友以《鬥陣特攻》中國籍英雄「小美」戴上口罩、宣導「光復香港，時代革命」的插圖回應官方。<br />\n<br />\n目前暴雪官方仍未宣布 11 月 2 日～3 日的暴雪嘉年華（BlizzCon 2019）是否有更動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/40742/blizzard-cancels-overwatch-on-switch-launch-party-at-nintendo-new-york\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F40742%2Fblizzard-cancels-overwatch-on-switch-launch-party-at-nintendo-new-york&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLHjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=8caee76e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/40742/blizzard-cancels-overwatch-on-switch-launch-party-at-nintendo-new-york</a>"},{"pid":"174aca42111b3efacc5cb0c932132b90270fdac7","tid":1656572,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:55:40.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"42af859a0ec54c26a765c43f0e93034b302d7ae2","tid":165657